<script>
window.addEventListener("load", (event) => {    
    setTimeout(function(){

        let h1 = document.querySelector('.full-screen-video-banner .content h1');        
        h1.style.transition = 'opacity 2s ease, margin .75s ease';
        h1.style.opacity = '1';
        h1.style.margin = '0 0 20px 0';

        let p = document.querySelector('.full-screen-video-banner .content p');  
        p.style.transition = 'opacity 2s ease';
        p.style.opacity = '1';

        let h4 = document.querySelector('.full-screen-video-banner .content h4');  
        h4.style.transition = 'opacity 2s ease';
        h4.style.opacity = '1';

        let a = document.querySelector('.full-screen-video-banner .content a');  
        a.style.transition = 'opacity 2s ease';
        a.style.opacity = '1';
        
        let headerDiv = document.querySelector('.header-wrapper');
        headerDiv.style.transition = 'opacity 1s ease, margin 1s ease';
        headerDiv.style.opacity = '1';
        headerDiv.style.margin = '0 0 0 0';

    }, 3000);    
});
</script>

settings.headline: 01A mentorship journey built for you, by you.
settings.paragraph: In the 1970s, the internet gave us a way to transcend the limits of standardized learning & local classrooms, opening the door to direct education from professionals worldwide.

settings.headline: 02A mentorship journey built for you, by you.
settings.paragraph:
Today, niche 'experts' rule the internet claiming to know what you need. But they don't. You’re the only expert on your vision for your life.

Forcing the student to squeeze into the box of ‘the curriculum’ is an outdated relic from the old-world education system.

settings.headline: 03A mentorship journey built for you, by you.
settings.paragraph: That’s why I created the worlds first dynamic coaching system; to put you in the drivers seat, while I ride shotgun holding accountable commitment and consistency.

settings.headline: 04A mentorship journey built for you, by you.
settings.paragraph: Start, dive in, or pause, at your pace, with the click of a button. Congratulations. Today is the day your story becomes yours.

settings.sub_title: Let’s get you fitted into something nice. How would you like to begin?
settings.desc: Whichever path you choose, you'll always be able to modify your plan before you commit.

settings.title: Your Compass
settings.desc:
Groundedness. Integration. Synthesis. Actionable insights and philosophies. Personal care and accountability to your goals.

When you work with me, it doesn’t matter if you’ve been studying, practicing, and healing for decades or if you just had your first mystical experience this morning. We have your entire life up until today to explore!

Why are you so self-aware yet so self-critical? Why are you so educated yet struggling to make it happen?

Why do you struggle to be proud of yourself?

Why are you contemplating buying plane tickets when you know that travel isn’t the best way to find yourself? What are you hiding from? And what’s hiding from you within your own life-story?

Let’s find out.

Your custom mentorship roadmap is waiting for you.

settings.title: Your Map
settings.desc:
A living library of proprietary resources inspired by my years of careful study. Over 15,000 pages of non-fiction read so you don’t have to. 10+ hours of video, 100+ downloadable PDF guides and workbooks, and so much more like readings, meditations, & hypnotherapy journeys and so much more…

Pain-stakingly woven into a net that can catch you no matter how hard you fall. Honed over 5 years based on the insights of 500+ SEM students who came before you.

Your bottomless search for self-improvement resoucres ends here. No more YouTube rabbit holes, aimless or forced journaling sessions, no more blank pages and blank minds unsure of what to do next. How much time have you thrown away while you try to ‘think things through’ by yourself?

You don’t need more time, you need more tools.

SEM contains 6 Straightforward Modules that create a unified system that allows you to face life head on, no matter what phase of life you’re in.

settings.title: My Mentorship Journeys
settings.desc: You're unique. Your support system should be too.
settings.bottom_desc: For the price of a single university class, I’ll help you integrate what you’ve learned into YOUR unique value proposition and find your own perfect place in the new world economy

settings.title: Who are my students?
settings.ready_desc:
• You are afraid of being judged/rejected for living an unconventional life
  • You're willing to follow your intuition in big ways
  • your healing journey is turning into a ‘healing loop’ and preventing you from building a fulfilling life
  • Your fear of failure holds you back from taking risks and trying new things.
  • You struggle with vulnerability, especially sharing your non-traditional goals
  • You resist asking for help or always wait for people to offer it
  • You worry that you don’t have the time, energy, or talent to achieve your goals
  • Feelings of inadequacy prevent you from being fully present in your work
  • You have a tendency to judge yourself harshly and get stuck in ‘critical spirals’
  • You crave deep sense of purpose and passion, driven by a desire to inspire and empower others, and contribute to a better world.
  • You feel alone or worry that you will feel more alone if you sharing your unique perspectives with loved ones who won’t understand.
  • You keep your true goals private to protect them, but it prevents you from working on them.
  • You’ve learned that traveling isn’t the only way to ‘find yourself’ and you’re ready to embark on an inner-journey.
settings.not_ready_desc:
• You aren’t ready to embrace change and reject societal norms that stifle individuality.
  • You are more committed to meeting others expectations than your own happiness
  • You believe that your doubts and fears are impossible to overcome
  • You’re not willing to take risks and embrace uncertainty for your individual growth and fulfillment.
  • You’re not fully committed to improving the quality and impact of your creative work.
  • You’re not someone who wants to challenge traditional norms and expectations.
  • You don’t believe that you can have more meaningful relationships

settings.desc:
"I started this program feeling lost, defeated, and down on myself about how much work I felt like l'd done, without tangibly seeing proof of my growth in the ways I wanted.

I knew what I loved doing, but I wasn't confident on the steps to take to get there. It was starting to feel impossible to overcome my blocks.

Your program helped me get grounded and grateful for my progress, highlighting deeply subconscious patterns that needed healing. The program left me with very practical tools on how to maintain that sense of purpose and drive throughout any endeavor I take on.

“ SEM is a doorway that allows us to explore our capabilities and get familiar with ourselves in a deeper and more organized way.

By the way of science, culture and spirituality, Nic offers an incredible yet simple resource for an empowering understanding of reality.

It helped me clarify my strengths and superpowers in a systematic way; and create a routine of rituals to guide me through my work as a person, an artist and a healer. ”

“ There was this lovely ongoing feeling that the program was made just for me.

Nic’s teachings always felt so synchronistic and applicable to me.

What I learned about myself and my journey is invaluable, the connections I made were deeper than relationships with people I consider closest to me.

I loved every part of this program and I am so grateful to my past self for making the decision to step into it. ”
